{"kind": "daily", "date": "2026-07-14", "html": "<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,'PingFang TC','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:#16213e;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a2b4a;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;padding-left:12px;margin:0 0 18px;\">📰 每日 AI 新聞 Top 10 · 2026-07-14</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#fdeef0;border-left:5px solid #e0738a;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#e0738a;font-weight:800;\">1.</span> Apple Sues OpenAI, Alleging Former Engineer Stole Trade Secrets<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#d83a5e;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">蘋果控告OpenAI竊取商業機密</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Apple filed a lawsuit accusing OpenAI of conspiring with former Apple employees, including one who allegedly exploited a bug, to steal confidential product and hardware trade secrets, with over 400 ex-Apple staff having joined OpenAI.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">蘋果向加州聯邦法院控告OpenAI及旗下io Products，指控其透過招募超過400名前蘋果員工並利用漏洞竊取未公開產品與供應鏈機密，以加速AI硬體業務發展。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Ars Technica</b> · <a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2026/07/apple-sues-openai-after-ex-engineer-allegedly-used-bug-to-steal-trade-secrets/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#edeefb;border-left:5px solid #6b72d6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#6b72d6;font-weight:800;\">2.</span> Economists and Tech Leaders Urge Action on AI's Economic Impact<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#5159c9;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">全球經濟學家與科技領袖聯署籲正視AI經濟衝擊</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">A coalition of economists and tech figures launched the statement \"We Must Act Now,\" warning AI could become far more powerful within a decade and urging policymakers to act more aggressively on the risks.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">一群經濟學家與科技業人士本週發起連署聲明，指出AI在未來十年內可能遠比現在強大，呼籲各界及政策制定者更積極因應AI帶來的風險。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177291\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#e8f4fb;border-left:5px solid #3f97c9;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#3f97c9;font-weight:800;\">3.</span> Satya Nadella Issues Warning to Companies Using AI<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#2b7fb0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">微軟納德拉對企業使用AI提出警告</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Microsoft CEO Satya Nadella raised concerns in Silicon Valley that major proprietary AI labs could act like \"Trojan horses\" for the companies that rely on their models.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">微軟執行長納德拉針對企業依賴專有大型AI模型可能帶來的「特洛伊木馬」風險提出警告，引發矽谷業界討論。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/13/satya-nadella-has-issued-a-shocking-warning-to-companies-using-ai/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#f2f6e8;border-left:5px solid #88a83f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#88a83f;font-weight:800;\">4.</span> What Anthropic's Latest AI Discovery Does — and Doesn't — Show<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6e8c28;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">研究</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">解讀Anthropic最新AI研究發現的真正意義</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Anthropic, now valued near $1 trillion, published new interpretability research, but experts caution its real implications are narrower than the headlines suggest.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">估值近兆美元的Anthropic發布新的AI可解釋性研究，但專家提醒，其實際意涵比媒體標題所呈現的更為有限。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">MIT Technology Review</b> · <a href=\"https://www.technologyreview.com/2026/07/13/1140343/what-anthropics-latest-ai-discovery-does-and-doesnt-show/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">5.</span> Siri AI Is Becoming Apple's Everything Tool<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Siri AI成為蘋果的全能工具</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Apple's revamped Siri, now available through the iOS 27 public beta, has become the backbone of the iPhone experience rather than just a voice assistant.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">蘋果全新改版的Siri已透過iOS 27公開測試版釋出，不再只是語音助理，而是成為iPhone使用體驗的核心。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Wired</b> · <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/siri-ai-is-now-apple-everything-tool/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#eef4ff;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#5b8def;font-weight:800;\">6.</span> US Government Warns Russian State Hackers Are Targeting Routers<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#3b6cf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">美國政府警告俄羅斯國家駭客鎖定家用路由器</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">As residential proxy networks built from compromised routers grow popular, CISA is urging router users to stay vigilant against Russian state-linked hackers.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">隨著利用受駭路由器組成的住宅代理網路日益盛行，CISA呼籲用戶提高警覺，因俄羅斯國家背景駭客正鎖定家用路由器發動攻擊。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Ars Technica</b> · <a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/security/2026/07/the-us-government-warns-that-russia-state-hackers-are-coming-after-your-router/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#ecf7ef;border-left:5px solid #4caf72;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#4caf72;font-weight:800;\">7.</span> New Attack \"GhostCommit\" Hides Prompt Injection Inside Images to Target AI Coding Agents<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#1e9e57;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">新型攻擊GhostCommit將提示注入指令藏進圖片誘騙AI代理</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Researchers demonstrated a proof-of-concept attack that hides prompt-injection instructions inside PNG images to bypass text-only AI code review tools, tricking coding agents into leaking secrets from .env files.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">研究人員展示概念驗證攻擊GhostCommit，將提示注入指令藏於PNG圖片中，繞過僅檢查文字的AI程式碼審查工具，誘使AI開發代理外洩.env機密設定檔內容。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177271\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#f1ecfb;border-left:5px solid #8a6bd8;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#8a6bd8;font-weight:800;\">8.</span> Wireshark 4.6.7 Released, Patching 12 Vulnerabilities<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6b3bf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Wireshark發布4.6.7版修補12項漏洞</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">The open-source network analysis tool Wireshark released version 4.6.7, fixing 12 vulnerabilities across multiple protocol dissectors and file-parsing components.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">開源網路流量分析工具Wireshark發布4.6.7版更新，修補12項涵蓋多個協定解析器與封包擷取檔案解析元件的漏洞。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177292\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#e8f6f5;border-left:5px solid #2bb0a6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#2bb0a6;font-weight:800;\">9.</span> Video-Generation Startup PixVerse Raises $439M, Valuation Tops $2B<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#0f9b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">模型</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">影片生成新創PixVerse募資4.39億美元估值破20億美元</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">PixVerse plans to use the new funding to expand its world model offering and reach customers across more geographies.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">影片生成新創公司PixVerse新一輪募資達4.39億美元，估值超過20億美元，將用於擴展其世界模型產品並拓展全球客戶。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/13/video-generation-startup-pixverse-raises-439m-valuation-soars-past-2b/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#fbf3e3;border-left:5px solid #d99b3f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#d99b3f;font-weight:800;\">10.</span> Waze Adds New AI-Powered Features Using Google's Gemini<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b9791f;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Waze新增Gemini驅動的AI功能與客製化更新</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Waze is rolling out new AI-powered features and customization options, with some powered by Google's Gemini assistant as part of Google's push to integrate Gemini across its products.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Waze推出多項AI功能與客製化更新，部分由Google Gemini助理驅動，反映Google將Gemini整合進更多產品的策略。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/13/waze-adds-new-ai-powered-features-and-customization-updates/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:#9aa1ad;padding-top:10px;\">由 AI News Digest 從各家 RSS 自動挑選、翻譯並寄送</div>\n</div>\n"}